      could accept unauthenticated connections despite CHAP users being set
    * Fix: VM path lookup stalled for 3 seconds before reporting error when
      multiple LUN records were found
    * Fix: pvesm set could silently clear user_password when called without
      providing a new value
    * Fix: Non-ASCII characters in volume names and sizes not fully stripped —
      only first occurrence was removed instead of all occurrences
    * Fix: jdssc clone operation logged a fatal error instead of reporting
      the actual failure when snapshot deletion was attempted during cleanup

